      "description": "$47,900 - Absolutely beautiful and exceptionally well-kept, this mint-condition car is the kind of find that\u2019s hard to come by. It presents beautifully inside and out, has clearly been cared for to a very high standard, and is ready for its next owner to enjoy. If you\u2019ve been searching for a standout example that needs nothing cosmetically, this one is well worth a look.",
