    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, good-condition vehicle that shows like a well-kept driver. It runs and drives well, presents nicely overall, and should make solid everyday transportation. The body and paint are presentable with the kind of light cosmetic wear and minor blemishes you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, and the interior is in good shape with normal signs of use but nothing excessive. This is not a mint collector-quality car, but it is a respectable, properly usable vehicle that a buyer can feel good about owning and driving.",
      "price": 33900.0,
