      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of opportunity, this vehicle is ideal for a handy buyer, first-time project owner, or anyone seeking affordable transportation with room to improve. It offers a solid value proposition at a low cost of entry, with usable components and plenty of potential for the right owner. If you want an inexpensive vehicle you can work on and make your own, this is a compelling option worth a closer look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little ride that could make a great starter car, commuter, or project. It has that affordable, no-nonsense appeal for someone who wants basic transportation without spending a fortune. If you don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, there\u2019s good value here.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with strong project potential. Runs, moves, and delivers the kind of mechanical feel enthusiasts appreciate, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a chassis that still feels usable around town. Not a show car, but a solid budget entry for someone who wants affordable transportation, a weekend wrenching platform, or a parts-friendly build candidate. Presents as a well-used vehicle with cosmetic wear consistent with age, but it has the kind of straightforward, serviceable character that makes it worth a look. If you want something inexpensive with real usability and room to improve, this one checks the box.",
      "price": 6450.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs and gets the job done. Used, rough around the edges, priced to move. Cheap entry car for someone who needs basic wheels now.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of lived-in charm that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who sees potential where others see ordinary\u2014a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel of something with real presence and a story to tell. Whether you\u2019re looking for a project, a practical runabout, or an affordable set of wheels with character, this one offers a chance to make it your own.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but for the right buyer it represents a practical opportunity for basic commuting, a first project, or an inexpensive backup vehicle. Priced to move and presented with honest value in mind.",
      "price": 4995.0,
